## Visual Standards (non-negotiable)
- All cards: border-radius 1.5rem+, border 1px rgba(36,247,255,0.25)
- Glass: bg rgba(6,16,36,0.3), blur(16px) saturate(1.35)
- Text: headers #e0f0ff, body #8ab4d8, data #24f7ff
- No sharp corners, no dark bg >0.45 alpha, no blur >20px

## Development Loop
1. Read TASK 0 (this file)
2. Pick highest priority item from CURSOR_TODO.md
3. Implement feature
4. Run `node skills/ion-dex-commander/scripts/audit-local-code.mjs`
5. Fix all FAIL issues
6. Commit with descriptive message
7. Auto-deploy: `node skills/ion-dex-commander/scripts/git-auto-deploy.mjs`

